#

Simple Vegetarian Borscht

45 min
$8
150 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

vegetarianlow-caloriegluten-free

Cuisine:

Eastern European

Course:

Soup

Tags:

soupeasyhearty

Description

A vibrant beetroot soup that's hearty and full of flavor, perfect for a cozy meal.

Ingredients

  • beets: 2 medium, peeled and grated
  • carrot: 1 large, grated
  • potato: 1 medium, diced
  • onion: 1 medium, chopped
  • cabbage: 2 cups, shredded
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • fresh dill: to taste (for garnish)
  • sour cream: for serving (optional)
